1. Compare the Triplets
------------------------------------------------

Link:
https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/compare-the-triplets/problem

Program to compare scores of two people.

def points(a, b):
    ap = 0
    bp = 0

    for i in range(3):
        if a[i] > b[i]:
            ap = ap + 1
        elif a[i] < b[i]:
            bp = bp + 1

    return ap, bp


Example

Input
5 6 7
3 6 10

Output
1 1


