2. A Very Big Sum
------------------------------------------------

Link:
https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/a-very-big-sum/problem

Program to calculate sum of large numbers.

def aVeryBigSum(ar):
    total = 0
    for i in range(len(ar)):
        total = total + ar[i]
    return total


Example

Input
5
1000000001 1000000002 1000000003 1000000004 1000000005

Output
5000000015


