3. Diagonal Difference
------------------------------------------------

Link:
https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/diagonal-difference/problem

Program to find difference between diagonals of a matrix.

def diagonalDifference(arr):
    sum1 = 0
    sum2 = 0
    n = len(arr)

    for i in range(n):
        sum1 = sum1 + arr[i][i]
        sum2 = sum2 + arr[i][n-1-i]

    return abs(sum1 - sum2)


Example

Input
3
11 2 4
4 5 6
10 8 -12

Output
15


