4. Plus Minus
------------------------------------------------

Link:
https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/plus-minus/problem

Program to find ratio of positive, negative and zero values.

def plusMinus(arr):
    n = len(arr)

    positive = 0
    negative = 0
    zero = 0

    for num in arr:
        if num > 0:
            positive += 1
        elif num < 0:
            negative += 1
        else:
            zero += 1

    print(f"{positive/n:.6f}")
    print(f"{negative/n:.6f}")
    print(f"{zero/n:.6f}")


Example

Input
6
-4 3 -9 0 4 1

Output
0.500000
0.333333
0.166667


